11-27-101. Definitions.

(a) As used in this act:

(i) "Board" means the Wyoming livestock board;

(ii) "Garbage" means putrescible animal and vegetable wastes resulting from the handling, preparation, cooking and consumption of foods including animal carcasses or parts thereof;

(iii) "This act" means W.S. 11-27-101 through 11-27-107.
